message.content:
I need to identify the line item that represents interest accrued but not yet received, and extract its initial and end values.

Looking at the balance sheet, the relevant line item would be "Interest Receivable", as this represents interest that has been earned but not yet collected.

From the balance sheet:
- Initial value of Interest Receivable on 2023-12-31: 0.00
- End value of Interest Receivable on 2024-02-05: 14796.43

These are the amounts of interest accrued but not yet received at the beginning and end of the reporting period.

```json
{"solution": {'initial value': '0.00', 'end value': '14796.43'}}
```
